# Security Policy

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you believe you have found a security vulnerability in **{{ cookiecutter.project_name }}**,
please report it privately. Do **not** open a public GitHub issue.

Email: [{{ cookiecutter.email }}](mailto:{{ cookiecutter.email }})

Please include:

- A description of the vulnerability and its potential impact.
- Steps to reproduce, or a proof-of-concept if available.
- Any suggested mitigations you are aware of.

You can expect an initial acknowledgement within five working days. We will
keep you informed as we investigate and work on a fix, and will coordinate
public disclosure with you once a patch is available.

## Supported Versions

Only the latest released version is actively supported with security fixes.
